id="v.iv.vi.x-p37.3"></span>

<span id="v.iv.vi.x-p38"></span> The <span class="Greek"><span
id="v.iv.vi.x-p38.1"></span>οἱ ἐπουράνιοι</span>, the “*de cœlo
homines*,” of this [1 Cor. 15.48](../../../bib/kjv/co1015.htm#048.md)<span
id="v.iv.vi.x-p38.2"></span> are Christ’s risen people; comp. [Phil.
3:20](../../../bib/kjv/phi003.htm#020.md),
[21](../../../bib/kjv/phi003.htm#021.md)<span id="v.iv.vi.x-p38.3"></span>
(Alford).

